{"article_id":"SoS1zsVJYWFPcnMW","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"' I wouldn ' t say","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"I ' m confident '","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that Congress will authorize action ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Obama said .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"|","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"REUTERS","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"Obama :","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"Strikes on hold","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"if Assad turns over WMDs","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"President Barack Obama would put strikes against Syria on hold","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"if Bashar Assad ' s regime were to turn over control of its chemical weapons ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"he said Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"as Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid announced","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"that he will wait to hear the president make his case to the nation Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"before holding an initial vote on military action .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"The moves came at the tail end of a tumultuous day for a White House","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that appeared to be knocked off-message by Secretary of State John Kerry ' s positive response to a question","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"about whether the administration would consider a proposal","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that would allow Syria to avoid a military strike","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"by turning over any stockpile of chemical weapons .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Obama said","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"he ' s open to","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"- though skeptical of -","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"a potential deal","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"to transfer control of Assad ' s weapons .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"\" Absolutely .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"If in fact that happens , \"","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Obama said in an interview with ABC , one of six","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"he sat for at the White House on Monday .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"The president said","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"his team will engage in talks with Russia and Syria .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"\" We ' re going to run this to ground , \"","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"he told CNN .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"\" And John Kerry and the rest of my national security team will engage with the Russians and the international community","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"to see","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"can we arrive at something","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"that is enforceable and serious . \"","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"These talks ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"he said in multiple interviews ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"could be a \" breakthrough , \"","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"but he said","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"the administration must move ahead skeptically .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"\" We don ' t want just a a stalling or delaying tactic","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"to put off the pressure","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"that we have on their right now , \"","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"he told NBC .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Though the plan seemed to emerge Monday","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"after Kerry , the secretary of state , mentioned the idea early in the day ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Obama said","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"the idea","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"of having Russia intervene","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"to try to get Syria to turn over control of its chemical weapons","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"has been on the table for more than a year .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"\" This is not new , \"","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"he told Fox News .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"\" I ' ve been discussing this with President Putin for some time now , \"","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"including conversations at last year ' s G-20 summit in Los Cabos , Mexico , and more recently .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"\" I did have those conversations \" last week at the G-2o in St. Petersburg , Russia ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"he told PBS .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Obama ' s interviews","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"- with ABC ' s Diane Sawyer , CBS ' s Scott Pelley , CNN ' s Wolf Blitzer , Fox News ' s Chris Wallace , NBC ' s Savannah Guthrie and PBS ' s Gwen Ifill -","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"capped off a day of remarks in support of a Syria strike from high-profile surrogates","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"including Kerry , former Secretary of State Hillary Clinton and National Security Adviser Susan Rice , as well as Rice deputies Tony Blinken and Ben Rhodes .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"The interviews also came","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"as the White House continued its outreach to members of Congress ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"bringing more than 70 to the West Wing on Monday ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"including most of the Congressional Black Caucus .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Obama had initially anticipated broad congressional support for a strike","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"and said as much in remarks as recently as late last week ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"but conceded Monday","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"that support isn ' t strong .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"\" I wouldn ' t say","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"I ' m confident \"","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that Congress will authorize action ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"he told NBC .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Just as Obama ' s interviews began to air at 6 p.m . ET ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"Reid announced","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"that he would hold off on filing cloture until after the president ' s speech to the nation ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"which is set for Tuesday at 9 p.m . ET .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"we need to see how fast we can do this .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"We have to see how well we can do this , \"","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Reid","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"( D-Nev. )","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"told senators .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"\" What we need to do is make sure","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"that the president has the opportunity","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"to speak to all 100 senators all 300 million people","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"before we do this . \"","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Reid said","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"he consulted with the president","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"before making his decision .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"The move could mean","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"the first procedural vote will occur as late as Thursday","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"without GOP cooperation .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"But Reid and Minority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"( R-Ky. )","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"could strike an agreement","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"to have a vote earlier , possibly Wednesday ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"when Reid had earlier predicted","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"the first vote would come .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"Obama said","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"he hasn ' t decided","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"whether he would go ahead with a strike","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"if Congress voted against it .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"it ' s fair to say","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"that I haven ' t decided .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"I am taking this vote in Congress and what the American people are saying very seriously , \"","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"If an agreement","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"to avert a military attack","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"can ' t be reached ,","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Obama acknowledged","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"in addition to swaying members of Congress ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"he also needs to convince the American people","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"- and even some in his own household -","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"that action is necessary .","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"\" I knew","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"by bringing this to Congress","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"that there was a risk","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"that the American people ,","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"you know ,","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"just could not arrive at a consensus around even a limited strike .","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"Because","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"if you ask somebody ,","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"you know ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"I read polls like everybody else , \"","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"he told NBC .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"\" And if you ask somebody ,","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"if you ask Michelle ,","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"' Do we do we want to be involved in another war ? '","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"The answer is no . \"","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"Early Monday , Kerry suggested a potential solution ,","depth":6},{"id":136,"text":"which Russia and Syria quickly seized on .","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"\" He could turn over every single bit of his chemical weapons to the international community in the next week .","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"Turn it over , all of it ,","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"without delay ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"and allow a full and total accounting for that , \"","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"he said , in response to a reporter ' s question .","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"\" But he isn ' t about to do it ,","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"and it can ' t be done , obviously . \"","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"Within hours , Russia and Syria both expressed interest in such a plan ,","depth":5},{"id":145,"text":"and","depth":6},{"id":146,"text":"even before Obama conducted his interviews ,","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"the administration said","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"it was open to considering an offer","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"but was \" highly skeptical \" of the Assad regime ' s promises ,","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"as Rhodes put it .","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"Kerry drew some criticism Monday","depth":6},{"id":152,"text":"when he suggested","depth":7},{"id":153,"text":"that a strike on Syria would be \" unbelievably small. \"","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"The White House later said","depth":6},{"id":155,"text":"that Kerry was contrasting the planned attack with larger military efforts such as the wars in Iraq and Afghanistan .","depth":6},{"id":156,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"that the phrasing reflects some error ,","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"it ' s a fact by comparison , \"","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"press secretary Jay Carney said .","depth":6},{"id":160,"text":"\" This is certainly much more limited and a smaller duration and size . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":321,"left":169,"right":320,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":169,"left":166,"right":168,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":166,"left":164,"right":165,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":163,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":162,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":162,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":165,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":6,"right":167,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":167,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":320,"left":294,"right":319,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":294,"left":219,"right":293,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":174,"right":218,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":171,"right":173,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":171,"left":170,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nucl